<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(برزة)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> قال: كان رسول اللَّه <span class="special">ﷺ</span> ينهى عن النوم قبل العشاء <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
